You must remember it

25
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,981
it is a very famous Cantonese melody

26
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,040
The song itself is about the potency

27
00:01:23,065 --> 00:01:25,190
of strength and
courage of these horses

28
00:01:27,633 --> 00:01:29,562
They escape the grasp of those that want

29
00:01:29,587 --> 00:01:30,687
claim to the land

30
00:01:30,611 --> 00:01:31,733
and if it wasn't the land

31
00:01:31,658 --> 00:01:33,588
it would be a claim to their bodies

32
00:01:33,613 --> 00:01:35,812
& they were forced to
always keep moving

33
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:38,844
Prevailing

34
00:01:38,869 --> 00:01:39,869
and so on

35
00:01:42,733 --> 00:01:46,000
You must remember this
song since it is very famous

36
00:01:46,566 --> 00:01:48,833
If I sing it for you,
you will recognize it

37
00:01:52,099 --> 00:01:54,420
When it gets translated
from Cantonese into English,

38
00:01:54,445 --> 00:01:56,057
it becomes a love song

39
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:03,733
This is the reason why Sin Ya asked
me to perform this song at her wedding

40
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:09,099
There's a subliminal quality to it

41
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:13,935
When the audience heard
the beginning notes, they

42
