them in the words coming from my mouth

49
00:02:49,066 --> 00:02:50,657
I was taking part

50
00:02:50,682 --> 00:02:51,582
in a violence

51
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,604
towards these horses

52
00:02:57,866 --> 00:02:59,592
And like a wave that
reaches it's crest

53
